source.name: Safety-Related Condition Reports (SRCRs) - 2002
source.description: As stipulated in '§191.25 for natural gas pipelines and '§195.56 for hazardous liquid pipelines, filing safety-related condition reports are required of each operator reporting safety-related conditions per '§191.23(a) or '§195.55(a).
